The Palo Alto High School boys' and girls' basketball teams played Wilcox High School this past Friday Jan. 30. The boys' team (13-4, 4-2) played against a Chargers team (6-10, 0-6) and ultimately prevailed with a 71-56 victory. The girls' team (16-2, 6-0) played the Wilcox girls’ team (3-13, 0-6) and pulled away in the second half with a 49-34 win.

